(59, 1, 7, 59, 4, 3, 3, 'receive any thing of the Lord', 'Connection on Receiving from God', 'Both passages emphasize the conditions for receiving from God. James 1:7 warns that one should not expect to receive anything from the Lord without proper faith, while James 4:3 explains that asking with selfish motives leads to not receiving.', 'theme', 0.398, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
